## Look Out
 - WTF-PAD adds padding as a pluggable transport
 - Break-Pad (Break‑Burst Padding) add padding directly to Tor and works has one-way and both-ways. "It works by sampling thresholds and padding‑burst sizes from probability distributions and inserting dummy “padding” packets whenever a long burst of incoming packets exceeds the threshold"